<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hard-adv">hard <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hɑːd/    美 /hɑːrd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>努力地；艰苦地</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I studied hard, for I didn't want to let Mum down.
我努力地学习，因为我不想让妈妈失望。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-heavily">2.★ <strong>猛烈地；重重地 (heavily)</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is <strong>raining hard</strong>. 
雨下得很大。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>harden /'hɑːdn/ v   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I stopped the ball and kicked it hardly back to the playground.  （2019全国 改错）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. hardly→hard  </p></div>